{
  "stem": "2713.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it was-- they had good information.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And one day, in the morning, we got out from the barracks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we could see the whole city was in darkness.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was daytime.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The Russians ever were coming closer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They were using some fog or some kind of-- and the whole part of the city was in darkness during the day.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they were coming through, the Russians.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we had an order to leave Czestochowa, the camp, as we were working.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Now, as I mentioned, we had the uniforms painted and the trousers painted.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So I had the jacket painted, as well.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] As we were walking, I once-- I mentioned before [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I could see that the Russians-- what they did, they came, the first offensive.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But they were staying there for a few months.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They didn't go any further.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was caught once already, nearly lost my life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I knew here it looked [INAUDIBLE] because you could see it as we were walking.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Ukrainians were guarding us very strictly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we could see the Germans running back and forth.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't really know what they were doing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I could see that it's really the end, that something is there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I knew that I've got my sister and my brothers most probably survived the war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then I'm going-- who knows where I'm going now?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I run in-- I manage to throw my jacket off myself.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I'm run into a toilet at the station.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was in the toilet for about five minutes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I must say-- no, sorry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When we were walking, that was when they took us first to a camp called Plzen.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
